## Summary

Relay already has a solid button system. I've documented it and added a few enhancements:

### Existing Button Classes
| Class | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| `.btn` | Base button style |
| `.btn.primary` | Cyan accent button |
| `.btn.success` | Green success button |
| `.btn.danger` | Red danger button |
| `.icon-btn` | 32x32 icon-only button |

### New Additions (in the reference)
| Class | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| `.btn.warning` | Orange warning button |
| `.btn.magenta` | Magenta accent |
| `.btn.purple` | Purple accent |
| `.btn.sm` / `.btn.lg` | Size variants |
| `.btn.ghost` | Transparent background |
| `.btn.pill` | Rounded pill shape |
| `.btn.loading` | Spinner animation |
| `.btn-group` | Grouped buttons |

